            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p align=\"center\" class=\"text-align-left\"><span class=\"font-size-medium\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>a)</strong></span> <span style=\"color:#000000;\">Lees de tekst over discriminatie</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">.</span></p>\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"text-align-left\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"text-align-left\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"font-size-medium\"><strong>b) </strong></span> <span class=\"font-size-medium\">Beantwoord de volgende vragen:</span></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"text-align-left\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"font-size-medium\">1)</span> <span class=\"font-size-medium\">Vertaal de onderstreepte woorden/zinnen naar het Engels.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"font-size-medium\">2)</span> <span class=\"font-size-medium\">Wat bedoelen we tegenwoordig met discriminatie?</span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-medium\" style=\"color:#000000;\">3) Wat is een zondebok?</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-medium\" style=\"color:#000000;\">4) Wat doet het Meldpunt Discriminatie?</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"font-size-medium\">5) Noem 6 voorbeelden van discriminatie die in de tekst worden</span> <span class=\"font-size-medium\">gegeven.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p>\n"
                },
                {
